parameters:
\nc<>I can finally rise to a higher position than a mere
believer!

\nc<>And not just a saint, but a high-ranking apostle. This is
all thanks to Kei-san!

\nc<>Even though Yukiko-chan was scared, they helped me and
saved the aunties, right? I think it was a very courageous
act.

\nc<>I-Is that so? Ehehe... Please continue to take care of me
from now on.

\nc<>This is my first time doing a job as a high-ranking member,
but somehow I feel like I can do it if I'm with Kei-san!

\nc<>Yukiko-chan is saying this, but I wonder what the reality
is.

\nc<>I don't think Kei's intuition is wrong, meow. They must have
hypnotized the ordinary believers too, that's why they rose
up, meow.

\nc<>That's right. Everyone seems to have completely forgotten
that the leader transformed into a villain....

\nc<>Since we've come this far, why don't we give it a try? Both
you and I are apostles, so we have the qualifications,
right?

\nc<>Yes, that's right! The leader also said to rely on you, so
please take care of us.

\nc<>To understand the true form of the Rakuenkyo cult that I am
not aware of, we should go up and see!
